data.description: River View!!! Your own Boat Landing!! Come check out this wonderful property located right on the Idaho and Oregon border. The 5.75 acre lot has so much room for animals, toys, outbuildings, or whatever you choose. There is already a 20x20 shop with power and also another metal machine shop for any equipment storage. When you walk into the home you'll notice a generous sized front room and a cozy pellet stove for those winter nights. The windows give a direct view out to the river and the access is easy to any bedroom and the kitchen area. There are some good updates with the flooring and metal roof. The back patio is perfect for enjoying the summer breezes and viewing the river. A major feature is the Snake River water rights that come with the property for irrigation. Water your yard, your pastures etc. Then head out onto the river for a little fishing anytime you want!! If you're looking for a small acreage that satisifies your outdoor enthusiasm, then look no further!!
